
# Custom profile: User-defined variable set (boilerplate)
#
# Define your own custom profile by adding variable names to line 1.
# Example:
#   VPN_SWITCH_TERMINAL_INTERPRETER VPN_SWITCH_COMBINATOR_INTERPRETER ...
#
# Available variables:
#   See .env-templates/ directory for all available configuration variables
#
# To start from an existing profile:
#   cat VPN_SWITCH_PROFILE_MINIMAL > VPN_SWITCH_PROFILE_CUSTOM
#   # Or
#   cat VPN_SWITCH_PROFILE_ALL > VPN_SWITCH_PROFILE_CUSTOM
#
# Then customize the list to match your needs.
#
# Usage:
#   vpn-switch bootstrap /path/to/base custom
